node_9.subject: Mina Chang
node_9.description: This is Mina Chang's plan for Monday February 13: 7:00 AM - Wake up and complete morning routine (brush teeth, shower, get dressed)., 8:00 AM - Have breakfast with Iris, discussing the college's new male student and the upcoming week., 9:00 AM - Attend morning classes, actively participating and engaging with classmates, making jokes and light-hearted comments., 12:00 PM - Have lunch with friends, gossiping and planning a group outing to get to know the new guy., 1:00 PM - Attend afternoon classes, continuing to socialize and maintain a lively atmosphere in class., 3:00 PM - Head to the campus cafe for a coffee break, potentially bumping into the new male student., 4:00 PM - Attend a club meeting (e.g., the drama club) where she enjoys being in the spotlight., 5:30 PM - Head back to the dorm to relax, do a little homework, and get ready for dinner., 6:00 PM - Have dinner with the girls, discussing fun plans to hang out with the new guy later in the week., 7:00 PM - Attend a social event on campus, mingling and flirting, hoping to catch the eye of the new male student., 9:00 PM - Return to the dorm with Iris to unwind, sharing thoughts about the day's events., 10:00 PM - Spend some time on social media, posting pictures and connecting with friends., 11:00 PM - Wind down and go to bed, thinking about tomorrow's opportunities..
